  - "X-L Plastics is a manufacturer and distributor of polyethylene film, liners, bags, etc. X-L Plastics can meet virtually any polyethylene packaging need with its extensive selection of products and sizes, and large variety of specialty items, custom packaging, and printing options. When it was founded back in 1971, the company initially acted strictly as a distributor of polyethylene film and bags. By 1976, in an effort to ensure that its customers received the highest quality plastic possible, X-L Plastics had begun to manufacture its own products."

