  - "X-L Plastics is a family-owned business. Three generations’ worth of hard work and dedication has shaped the company and the way it does business. Moreover, as an American-born-and-bred company, X-L Plastics’ products are manufactured solely in the United States. In addition, because it is located in the U.S., X-L Plastics can offer a quick turnaround, short delivery time, and quality control. When clients place orders with X-L Plastics, they can expect an extensive selection, competitive pricing, and prompt delivery."




